China Asks Nanning to Increase Affordable Housing Construction

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-10-17T02:20:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-17/china-asks-nanning-to-increase-affordable-housing-construction.html
China’s State Council asked Nanning
city to increase affordable housing construction in its short-
term urban development plan, according to a statement posted on
the central government’s website today.  The central government also required the capital city of
the southwestern Guangxi region to restrict the development of
energy-intensive industries, according to the statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gregory Turk at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  